sequenceDiagram
    participant Index as Models Index<br/>YAML Files
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>Go CLI
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as OCI Registries<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Output as Output Directory<br/>File I/O
    participant Catalog as Catalog YAML<br/>data/*.yaml
    participant Container as Data Container<br/>UBI9-minimal
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>Volume Mount

    Note over Index,Catalog: Flow 1: Model Catalog Generation Pipeline (CI/CD)

    Index->>Extractor: Read data/models-index.yaml
    Extractor->>HF: GET /api/collections/{id}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token (optional)
    HF-->>Extractor: Collection models list
    Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{repo}/manifests/{tag}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Public pull
    Registry-->>Extractor: OCI manifest + modelcard layer
    Extractor->>Extractor: Extract modelcard YAML frontmatter<br/>Parse metadata fields
    Extractor->>HF: GET /api/models/{id}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token (optional)
    HF-->>Extractor: Model details, README, license, tags
    Extractor->>Extractor: Multi-source priority enrichment<br/>HF YAML > HF API > modelcard > regex > defaults
    Extractor->>Extractor: Match vLLM recommended configs<br/>by HuggingFace model name
    Extractor->>Output: Write metadata.yaml, enrichment.yaml<br/>per model
    Extractor->>Catalog: Write data/models-catalog.yaml<br/>Deduplicated, enriched

    Note over Index,Catalog: Flow 2: MCP Server Catalog Generation (CI/CD)

    Index->>Extractor: Read data/redhat-mcp-servers-index.yaml
    Extractor->>Extractor: Read input/mcp_servers/redhat/*.yaml<br/>Static MCP server definitions
    Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{mcp-repo}/manifests/{tag}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Public pull
    Registry-->>Extractor: OCI config (architectures, timestamps)
    Extractor->>Catalog: Write data/redhat-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml

    Note over Container,Dashboard: Flow 3: Runtime Data Delivery

    Catalog->>Container: COPY data/*.yaml /app/data/<br/>Docker build (no runtime build)
    Container->>Dashboard: Volume mount /app/data/<br/>Init container or sidecar
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Read catalog YAML files<br/>Populate model catalog UI
